<br>
Nice thing about Vindi, is he's easy to find out. 8 hour spawn, don't have to look real hard for something to kill. Most other things are 3, 4.5-5, or 7 day spawns, and go down quick as snot. Sounds like your guild is in little position to race/rush towards a mob when yuo see it up. <br>
<br>
For a guild in your position, Vindi has a ton of plusses. He's a fun fight, you can learn a TON from him, he's not hard to find up, he's not hard to get to, rarely have to race/rush for him, you can take your time, you can do him about every night of the week if you want to, and on top of it all, he's got some damn nice gear drops.<br>
<br>
